text: Julia Sanchez Parma (born 14 December 1990) is an Argentine professional racing cyclist. She rides for the Itau Shimano Ladies Power Team. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
